graph TB
    subgraph "ODH Dashboard Pod"
        Frontend[React Frontend<br/>PatternFly UI]
        Backend[Node.js Backend<br/>Fastify Server<br/>Port: 8080/TCP]
        OAuthProxy[OAuth Proxy Sidecar<br/>Port: 8443/TCP HTTPS]

        Frontend -.->|served by| Backend
        OAuthProxy -->|proxies to| Backend
    end

    subgraph "Custom Resources (CRDs)"
        AccelProfile[AcceleratorProfile<br/>dashboard.opendatahub.io/v1]
        OdhApp[OdhApplication<br/>dashboard.opendatahub.io/v1]
        DashConfig[OdhDashboardConfig<br/>opendatahub.io/v1alpha]
        OdhDoc[OdhDocument<br/>dashboard.opendatahub.io/v1]
        QuickStart[OdhQuickStart<br/>console.openshift.io/v1]
    end

    subgraph "External Dependencies"
        K8sAPI[Kubernetes API Server<br/>443/TCP HTTPS]
        OAuth[OpenShift OAuth<br/>443/TCP HTTPS]
        Prometheus[Prometheus/Thanos<br/>9091/TCP HTTPS]
        ImageReg[OpenShift Image Registry<br/>443/TCP HTTPS]
    end

    subgraph "ODH/RHOAI Components"
        KServe[KServe<br/>serving.kserve.io]
        Notebooks[Kubeflow Notebooks<br/>kubeflow.org]
        DSC[DataScienceCluster<br/>datasciencecluster.opendatahub.io]
        Builds[OpenShift Builds<br/>build.openshift.io]
    end

    User[User Browser] -->|HTTPS/443<br/>Bearer Token| OAuthProxy

    Backend -->|watches/manages| AccelProfile
    Backend -->|watches| OdhApp
    Backend -->|manages| DashConfig
    Backend -->|watches| OdhDoc
    Backend -->|watches| QuickStart

    Backend -->|REST API<br/>ServiceAccount Token| K8sAPI
    OAuthProxy -->|validates tokens| OAuth
    Backend -->|queries metrics| Prometheus
    Backend -->|queries imagestream layers| ImageReg

    Backend -->|manages ServingRuntimes| KServe
    Backend -->|creates/manages Notebook CRs| Notebooks
    Backend -->|watches status| DSC
    Backend -->|triggers builds| Builds

    style Frontend fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style Backend fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style OAuthProxy fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style AccelProfile fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333
    style OdhApp fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333
    style DashConfig fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333
    style OdhDoc fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333
    style QuickStart fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333
